程序包 yt.tojava.taskmanager

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Deadline
    Represents a deadline task that to be done by a specific date/time.
    Parser
    Parser class containing methods that deals with parsing the user command to extract meaningful details from it.
    Storage
    Storage class that will help to load Tasks from the hard disk and save tasks to the hard disk
    Task
    Task class contains task description, task status
    TaskList
    TaskList class that is responsible for keeping the in-memory task list.
    Todo
    ToDo : a task to do someday Todo class inherit from Task class
    Ui
    Ui class that will be responsible for interacting with the user.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    FileNotFoundException
    FileNotFoundException class that inherits the Exception class Override the constructor that takes a String parameter so that you can specify the error information when you create a FileNotFoundException object.
    TaskManagerException
    TaskManagerException class that inherits the Exception class Override the constructor that takes a String parameter so that you can specify the error information when you create a TaskManagerException object.
